H0.text: What is the collective noun for a group of frogs. Chorus

H1.text: What is the collective noun for a group of frogs. Leap

H2.text: What is the collective noun for a group of frogs. Pond

H3.text: What is the collective noun for a group of frogs. Army

A4.text: The assembled frogs may call in unison and frenzied activity ensues, the males scrambling to mate with the usually smaller number of females.
